%90%E8%A3%9C%E7%B5%A6%E9%BB%9E\">食材補給點</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E4%BA%8B%E9%A0%85\">其他事項</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91\">現金</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E5%85%85%E9%9B%BB\">充電</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E9%80%9A%E8%A8%8A%E9%BB%9E\">通訊點</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E6%95%91%E6%8F%B4%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC\">救援號碼</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E6%92%A4%E9%80%80%E9%BB%9E\">撤退點</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#app-gps\">APP GPS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99\">相關其他資料</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E6%9C%AC%E9%9A%8A%E5%A4%A5%E4%BC%B4\">本隊夥伴</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E5%AD%9F%E6%A8%BA%EF%BC%88%E9%A0%98%E9%9A%8A%E5%B1%B1%E5%B1%8B%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%EF%BC%89\">孟樺（領隊&#x26;山屋申請）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E6%B3%8A%E7%91%9C%EF%BC%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%9A%EF%BC%89\">泊瑜（大廚）</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E5%AD%90%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%88%E5%9A%AE%E5%B0%8E%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%EF%BC%89\">子心（嚮導&#x26;紀錄）</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%90\">行程總結</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E5%9B%B0%E9%9B%A3%E5%BA%A6%E2%98%85%E2%98%85%E2%98%85%E2%98%85\">困難度★★★★</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E7%B8%BD%E8%8A%B1%E8%B2%BB\">總花費</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E8%A3%9D%E5%82%99%E6%B8%85%E5%96%AE\">裝備清單</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB\">糧食計畫</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E8%A1%8C%E5%89%8D%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99\">行前準備</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E6%B2%BF%E9%80%94%E7%8B%80%E6%B3%81\">沿途狀況</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#%E7%93%A6%E6%96%AF%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C\">瓦斯問題</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/mountain/GR20%20%E6%94%BB%E7%95%A5/#15%E5%A4%A9%E9%A3%9F%E6%9D%90%E6%B8%85%E5%96%AE%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E4%BB%BD%EF%BC%89\">15天食材清單（三人份）</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"世界徒步攻略｜科西嘉島 GR20 縱走之旅","type":"blog","date":"Jul 21, 2019","tags":["那些年我們去縱走","GR20"],"category":"旅行日記","log":null,"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.497797356828194,"src":"/static/f6e08df41836038207ecd3aec8ed33c9/45677/cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f6e08df41836038207ecd3aec8ed33c9/722c4/cover.jpg 340w,\n/static/f6e08df41836038207ecd3aec8ed33c9/1d671/cover.jpg 680w,\n/static/f6e08df41836038207ecd3aec8ed33c9/45677/cover.jpg 843w","sizes":"(max-width: 843px) 100vw, 843px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/mountain/GR20 攻略/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/筆記｜參觀奧斯維辛集中營/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"當我走入波蘭的奧斯維辛集中營","tags":["筆記"],"date":"2019-06-10","category":"旅行日記","mark":null,"description":null,"log":null}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/weekly journal/選擇與接受/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"#7 選擇與接受","tags":["life"],"date":"2019-07-23","category":"Weekly Journal","mark":null,"description":null,"log":null}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"]}